appDesc:
Gradulator - GCUF GPA/CGPA is a free and easy to use GPA/CGPA calculator for GCU (Main, Sub campuses and affiliated colleges) using which you don't have to go through all the calculations to calculate your GPA/CGPA and quality points of all subjects individually. This simple tool will help you get through easily. All you have to do is to fill the required fields and this tool will generate a full result card having quality points, grades and percentage etc.
This app strictly follows the GPA & CGPA calculation criteria as per Government College University (Main & Sub campuses) with user-friendly interface.
appShortDesc: Accurate and elegant tool which calculates GPA/CGPA of semester(s) of GCU.
features: GPA Calculation upto 10 subjects
CGPA Calculation upto 10 semesters
Save calculated result card in an organized way or export it to the gallery.
Share your result card with your friends and family instantly.
Attractive and user-friendly interface to understand the whole application and operate easily.

Huge collection of captions and status

Share/Copy on social media apps like Facebook, Instagram, and Whats App
